en: Hello ! Please mention the channel you want to host the giveaway in. !

Super! How long do you want the giveaway to last? 
 You can use `m` for minutes, `h` for hours, `d` for days.

How many winners will this giveaway have? 
 Please enter a number between `1` and `10`.

Good. What is the prize of this giveaway? 
 Please enter the giveaway prize under this message.

How many messages do giveaway participant need to have? 
 Answer `0` to skip this step.

How many invites do giveaway participant need to have? 
 Aswer `0` to skip this step.
Hello ! start by giving me the **channel** which once joined will have to create a temporary channel (vocal channel only) !
Great! and now, in which category should I create the temporary channels? give a channel ID or name!
Wonderful ! and how many people maximum will be able to go in these temporary channels ? ( give a number between 1 and 10 )
Hello ! start by giving me the **channel** that will trigger the system response. If you want it to work on the whole server, put `all`.
Great! Now give me the text that will trigger the response. If you want it to be triggered on every message, type `every`.

Wonderful! And now give me the text I should send in response.
**Help**:
`{user}`: mentions the user.

Okay! And now, after how long do you want to delete the reply. If you don't want to delete the message, send `no`.
 You can use `s` for seconds, `m` for minutes, `h` for hourss
And finally, do you want the message that triggered the action to be deleted? Answer with `yes` or `no`.
Hello ! start by giving me the **channel** that will trigger the system response. If you want it to work on the whole server, put `all`.
Great! Now give me the text that will trigger the reaction. If you want it to be triggered on every message, type `every`.
Beautiful! And now give me the emoji I'll have to react with.
Hello ! start by telling me if I should activate or deactivate the goodbye system. Answer with (**enable** or **disable**) !
Great! Now what channel should I send your message to? Give a text channel.

Wonderful! But now let's focus on the message I'll have to send.
**Help**:
`{user}` : Mentions the user
`{tag}` : Puts the tag of the user ( ex : Pauldb09#0001)
`{username}` : Puts the username of the member
`{server}` : Puts the name of the server
`{counter}` : Puts the number of members of the server
Right. But in what form should I send it? If you want a picture, send **image** and if you just want the text, send: **text**.
Hello ! start by telling me if I should activate or deactivate the welcome system. Answer with (**enable** or **disable**) !
Great! Now what channel should I send your message to? Give a text channel.

Wonderful! But now let's focus on the message I'll have to send.
**Help**:
`{user}` : Ping the user
`{username}` : Put the user's name of the member
`{server}` : Put the name of the server
`{counter}` : Puts the number of members of the server
`{inviter}` : Puts the person who invited the member
`{invites}` : Puts the number of invitations of the person who invited the member
Right. But in what form should I send it? If you want a picture, send **image** and if you just want the text, send: **text**.
Hello! start by giving me the **channel** where I will send this panel!
Great! and now, give me the support role that will have access to this panel
Wonderful! And now give me a title for this panel (the reason why users open a ticket)
Right. And what will be the description of this panel (the message on the embed inviting users to create a ticket)
Right. And in which category should I create the tickets? Give me the name of a category or its ID.

Everything is ok. But you have to give the message that will welcome the members in their ticket 
**Help**:
`{user}` : Mentions the user.
Hello ! start by telling me if I should activate or deactivate the auto ping system. Answer with (**enable** or **disable**) !
Great! Now what channel should I send your message to? Give a text channel.

Wonderful! But now let's focus on the message I'll have to send.
**Help**:
`{user}` : Ping the user

Okay! And now, after how long do you want to delete the message.
 You can use `s` for seconds, `m` for minutes.
Hello ! start by telling me if I should enable or disable messages during a boost. Answer with (**enable** or **disable**) !
Great! Now what salon should I send your message to? Give a text channel.

Wonderful! But now let's look at the message I will have to send.
**Help**:
`{user}` : Ping the userr
`{tag}` : Put the user's tag ( ex : Pauldb09#0001)
`{username}` : Put the user's username
`{server}` : Put the name of the server
Right. And what role will I have to give to the people who boost the server?
Hello ! start by telling me if I should activate or deactivate the youtube alerts system. Answer with (**enable** or **disable**) !
Great! Now what channel should I send your message to? Give a text channel.

Wonderful! But now let's focus on the message I'll have to send.
**Help**:
`{YoutuberName}` : Give the name of the youtuber who made the video
`{videoName}` : Give the name of the video that has just been released.
`{VideoURL}` : Give the link of the video.
Good. Now give me the name of the youtuber that I will follow. Give the link of a channel or the name.
